column1: # Title: Onshore Wind Resource Potential by ReEDS Wind Region; Class; and Bin

# Comments: Onshore wind resource potential in MW for each region-class-bin. Bins are the portions of the interconnection supply curves. Summing across bins will provide total resource in a region and class.
# Source: Information based on ReEDS version 2017.  Files provided by ReEDS team in April 2017.
